This is scheduled to be removed in Gradle 10.0. Use assignment ('ndkVersion = <value>') instead. Properties should be assigned using the 'propName = value' syntax. Setting a property via the Gradle-generated 'propName value' or 'propName(value)' syntax in Groovy DSL has been deprecated. This is scheduled to be removed in Gradle 10.0. Use assignment ('signingConfig = <value>') instead.
